activity.text: Hi, I am Mohamed Mushraf, a final year Computer Science and Engineering Undergraduate. I would like to take part in this GSoC project, since it is aligning with my current technical skills and expertise. By contributing to this project, I am looking forward to start my open source journey along with contributing to the society. I would like to know, what is expected in the proposal and some guidance on preparing it. Thank you.
